    public class VMResponseGeneratorOutboundPort
extends fr.upmc.components.ports.AbstractOutboundPort
implements ResponseArrivalI
    The class VMResponseGeneratorOutboundPort implements the outbound port for a given component.

    Description

    The port implements the ResponseArrivalI interface as required and upon a call, passes it to the connector that must also implement the same interface.

    Invariant

     invariant      true
